Written 2026-07-22 to close a real gap: this repo, and its sibling colonies
4DBRAIN and aether, had no LICENSE file at all until now, meaning even the
hive's own other repos had no formal grant to reuse this code across repo
boundaries despite common authorship. This file formalizes what was already
true in practice, and unblocks the colony_sdk consolidation and tesseract-
math relocation work described in memory/planning/ (THEHIVE repo) without
changing anything about who owns this code or what it may be used for
outside the federation.
